A sophisticated 2D/3D game framework for Mac OS X and iPhone.


<< How to build >>

1. Change version string in Karakuri_Defines.h.
2. Open the project in Xcode.
3. Build "Build & Install All" for Debug.
4. Build "Bulid & Install All" for Release.


<< How to make an installer >>

1. Do "build" at first.
2. Copy "Karakuri Library/build/Universal/Karakuri" folder to "Installer/Karakuri Library/Contents".
3. Execute Installer/set_permission_all.sh script in Terminal.
4. Open all package projects in Package Maker bundled in Xcode 2.5.
5. Build all packages.
6. Move a library package, project template packages and file template packages into the framework package.
7. Now publish the framework package.


